*** Direct use ***

1. Simply copy the Capture2Net.exe file to any location you want.
   Note: You need write permissions to that folder to save the configuration and history!

2. Start the program and configure it as you like (Shortcuts, file names, WebDAV connection details, etc.).

3. Create some screenshots



*** Compiling the source ***

Capture2Net is written in PureBasic 4.60. You have to buy PureBasic in order to compile the source your self.

More information about PureBasic and how to get it on http://www.purebasic.com